{"tid":910912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持警察開鎗","createTime":"2018-11-21T13:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T13:38:35.000Z","uid":209890,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41b1a76ff53484b169b7262dee9c8b5670a4f64b","tid":910912,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:30:34.000Z","msg":"雖然對警察都無好感架喇<br />\n特別抄鳩我牌果陣<br />\n但兒登仔醒下啦<br />\n應該對事唔對人<br />\n拎住把刀衝埋黎<br />\n警告過仲衝埋黎<br />\n一鎗打爆你個頭都仲得啦<br />\n有玩過氣鎗都知<br />\n其實要射中手依d會移動既目標係好高難度<br />\n所以射身係最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n比人用刀插中 死左比兒登仔笑<br />\n開鎗射死個持刀者 死左比兒登仔屌<br />\n<br />\n刀既破壞力好勁<br />\n插中頸致死機率好大"},{"pid":"ab4ae398692e54644d3f2f3acf06635ae9e6ba8d","tid":910912,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">木</span>倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399c9cf7441aef03cfadbf9166406d381de401ef","tid":910912,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ab4ae398692e54644d3f2f3acf06635ae9e6ba8d","tid":910912,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">木</span>倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"一直都以為鎗tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}